# Personal Finance Tracker

A full-stack Personal Finance Tracker web application that helps users manage their daily expenses, monthly budget, and savings goals with visual analytics.

---

##  Features

-  User Authentication (Login / Signup with JWT)
-  Add, Edit, Delete Expenses
-  Month-wise Expense Filtering
-  Visual Charts (Pie, Donut, Bar Graphs)
-  Monthly Budget Management
-  Short-term & Long-term Goals
-  Dashboard with Analytics
-  PDF Report Download
-  User Profile with Photo Upload
-  CSV Auto Import of Expenses

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

### Frontend:
- React.js  
- React Router  
- Chart.js + react-chartjs-2  
- Papaparse (CSV Import)  
- html2canvas & jsPDF (PDF Reports)  
- CSS (Custom Styling)

### Backend:
- Node.js  
- Express.js  
- MongoDB + Mongoose  
- JWT Authentication  
- Multer / Base64 for Image Upload  

---

